    <descript>
      <abstract>The Polygon feature represents all hydrology features greater than five feet in width.</abstract>
      <purpose>Use this feature to identify all lakes, rivers, and streams that are greater than five feet in width.  Hydrology features less than five feet in width are captured as a line feature.</purpose>
